'''Lesley Lawson''' nÃ©e '''Hornby''' (born 19 September 1949) known as ''' Twiggy''' is an [[English people|English]] [[model (person)|model]], actress, and singer. In the early-1960s she became a prominent British teenage model of [[swinging sixties]] London with others such as [[Penelope Tree]].
